data.title: SA actor from 'Brooklyn Nine-Nine' in new Stephen King movie & Apple TV+ series
data.meta_description: Antonio Raul Garcia, who you might know as "Nikolaj" (no, NI-ko-laj) from the hit TV show "Brooklyn Nine-Nine," shares his love for his hometown of San Antonio and gives us the deets on two major new projects.
data.text:
Published: August 6, 2024 at 5:13 PMUpdated: August 6, 2024 at 5:20 PM

Antonio Raul Garcia, who you might know as "Nikolaj" (no, NI-ko-laj) from the hit TV show "Brooklyn Nine-Nine," shares his love for his hometown of San Antonio and gives us the deets on two major new projects.
